SCREENS STRUCTURE:

1. Home Screen
   - Royal Mix Global overview
   - Quick access to all modules
   - Royal Mix Choco featured as "Living Product"

2. Royal Mix Choco Dashboard
   - Product identity & philosophy
   - "It is for intelligence, not fat"
   - Active regions (e.g. Chawama – Testnet)

3. Products Screen
   - Royal Mix Choco (dry snack)
   - Royal Mix Choco Drink
   - Royal Mix Tobwa (children & adults)
   - Future nutrition products
   (All powered by one base system)

4. Production Logic Screen
   - Dry roasting & baking logic
   - Modular process (manual → semi-industrial)
   - Shelf-life intelligence (12–24 months roadmap)

5. Packaging & Market Screen
   - Testnet packaging (round buckets)
   - Phase 2 packaging (rectangle buckets)
   - Cost & visibility strategy

6. Agent System Screen
   - Agent registration
   - Uniform & branding guidelines
   - Daily activity reporting
   - Stock movement tracking

7. Shop Loyalty Screen
   - Shop registration
   - Purchase history
   - Bonus ladder visibility
   - Loyalty status

8. Bonus & Incentives Screen
   - Volume-based bonuses
   - Weekly / monthly cycles
   - Agent-managed bonus flow

9. Testnet Analytics Screen
   - Daily sales
   - Road-by-road performance
   - Shop engagement metrics
   - Product velocity

10. Community & Trust Screen
   - Testimonials
   - Local market visuals
   - Community impact metrics
